description:
Enter the haunted corridors of the Space Hulk in Tacticus' Halloween update!
Face endless waves of Genestealers and Tyranids in Survival Mode, and join the Sororitas and Black Templars against the Death Guard in a new Campaign event!

Tacticus now features over 95 Champions across 20 Factions — play now!
